summary:
Experienced Sales and Branch Manager in Heavy Duty Automotive parts with in depth knowledge of parts for MAN, Volvo, Scania, Mercedes-Benz, DAF, Iveco, Diesel Technic and Kolbenschmidt

Strong leader of sales teams:
- providing guidance, training and mentorship
- setting sales quotas and goals
- creating sales plans
- analyzing data
- assigning sales territories
- building the team
- procurement and management of stock
